ansalaska pipeline system contents  corporate history  early history  diversification and restructuring  recent history  organization  services  notable projects  see also  references  external links corporate historyedit early historyedit headquarters of fluor bros construction in the early s fluor corporations predecessor rudolph fluor  brother was founded in  by john simon fluor and his two brothers in oshkosh wisconsin as a saw and paper mill john fluor acted as its president and contributed  in personal savings to help the business get started the company was renamed fluor bros construction co in  in  john fluor moved to santa ana california for health reasons without his brothers and founded fluor corporation out of his garage under the name fluor construction company by  the business had annual revenues of   million in  dollars and a staff of  employees john fluor delegated most of the companys operations to his sons peter and simon fluor a  capital investment was made that year and it was incorporated johns eldest son peter served as head of sales and grew the company to  million  million in  dollars in revenues by  in  the company reincorporated as fluor corporation by the s fluor had operations in europe the middle east and australia business declined rapidly during the great depression but picked up again during world war ii during the war fluor manufactured synthetic rubber and was responsible for a substantial portion of highoctane gasoline production in the united states a gasgasoline division of fluor was created in houston in  fluors headquarters were moved to los angeles in  in order to be closer to its oil and gas clients before moving again to orange county california in the s due to concerns about the cost of living and traffic john simon fluor died in  he was succeeded by his son peter fluor who died three years later peter was followed by shirley meserve  and donald darnell  then john simon si fluor jr in  and j robert bob fluor in  fluor was listed on the new york stock exchange in the s in  fluor acquired an interest in construction design and contracting firm william j moran diversification and restructuringedit fluor diversified its business more extensively in  when five companies were merged into a division called coral drilling and it started a deepwater oil exploration business in houston called deep oil technology it also created fluor ocean services in houston in  and acquired an interest in other fossil fuel operations in the s fluor acquired a construction company pike corp of america and the engineering division of its prior partner in australia utah construction in  fluor bought land in irvine california and started building its new headquarters on it the following year the companys oil and gas operations were consolidated under a new entity fluor oil and gas corp in  fluor acquired daniel international corporation fluors business had become predominantly international while daniel internationals  billion construction business was mostly domestic the acquisition allowed the company to use union labor at fluor or nonunion labor at daniel for each client fluor made a  billion acquisition of a zinc gold lead and coal mining operation st joe minerals in  after a bidding competition for the business with seagram by the s fluors primary business was building large refineries petrochemical plants oil pipelines and other facilities for the gas and oil industry especially in the middle east by  fluors staff had grown to  and revenue backlog and profits had each increased more than  percent over the prior year however by  the mining operation was causing heavy losses and the oil and gas industry fluor served was in a worldwide recession due to declining oil prices from  to  fluors backlog went from  billion to  billion in  it reported  million in losses david tappan took bob fluors place as ceo in  after bob died from cancer and led a difficult restructuring the company sold  million in assets includi