econdlargest copper mine in the world in  fluor constructed cooling towers and other facilities in hanford washington for the manhattan project it built an expansion of the dhahran aire force base in saudi arabia for the united states army in the s and accepted its first international project for aramco in the middle east in the s and s fluor built the first allhydrogen refinery in kuwait and the first exclusively offshore power plant for the atlantic richfield company it also constructed pumps and ports for the transalaska pipeline system which traversed  miles from northern alaska to valdez alaska and the worlds largest offshore facility for natural gas on the island of java in indonesia in  it was awarded a  billion project for aramco in saudi arabia to design facilities that capture sour gas which is expelled from oil wells as waste in order to refine it into fuel that same year a partially completed copper and cobalt mine in africa was cancelled due to a war in the neighboring region of angola and declining copper prices in  fluor had  projects for building united states power plants and had served more than half of the worlds governmentowned oil companies fluor workers at a radiation cleanup site in ohio fluor has been working on the cleanup and shutdown of atomic energy plants in ohio and washington since the s in  fluor won a contract with the united states energy department to clean up nuclear waste by  hanford was the most contaminated nuclear site in the us and the us department of energy was conducting a  billion to  billion cleanup of the site fluor hanford inc replaced westinghouse hanford co on the project after a chemical explosion in   workers filed a lawsuit alleging they were denied appropriate medical attention and protective gear fluor and the workers disagreed on whether the explosion resulted in any injuries in  the us department of energy fined fluor for safety violations and that same year a jury awarded  million in damages to  pipe fitters 